Mission Accomplished 💐 Happy heavenly birthday to ancestor Maya Angelou.⁠
⁠
Maya Angelou didn’t just survive, she thrived... leaving behind a legacy of wisdom and artistry that continues to inspire generations. As a poet, author, and activist, she used her words to uplift, empower, and ignite change.⁠
⁠
Today, on her heavenly birthday, we honor her brilliance and the light she shared with the world. 🙌🏾⁠
